Package: plasticRank
Title: Rank and Visualize Country-Level Environmental Indicators
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mason", "Souza", , "mpsouza@calpoly.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Ryan", "Bruning", , "rbruning@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Will", "Mathewson", , "wfmathew@calpoly.edu", role = "aut"))
Description: Provides functions to load, clean, summarize, and visualize a
    merged dataset of plastic waste audit data (TidyTuesday 2021) combined
    with GDP, population, and CO2 emissions data. Countries can be ranked
    and compared across environmental and economic indicators for 2019-2020.
